<div class="requirements-show">
  <style>
  table, th, td {
      border: 1px solid black;
      width: 500px;
  }
  th, td {
      padding: 15px;
  }
  </style>

  <h1>A-G Requirements</h1>
  <p>
    To attend a University of California (UC) or a California State University(CSU),
    all high school students need to complete the A-G requirements. The following
    are a list of the required subjects and number of years.
  </p>
  <p>
    You must receive a grade of C or better. You can also use test scores. The classes must<br>
    be from the approved list.
    Click <a href="http://admission.universityofcalifornia.edu/freshman/requirements/a-g-requirements/">here</a>
    for more information from UC website.
  </p>
  <% if current_user %>
    <p>
      <%=link_to "Click here if you would like to use our A-G Tracker", user_requirements_path(current_user)%>
    </p>
  <% else %>
    <p>
      <%=link_to "Click here if you would like to use our A-G Tracker", login_path %>
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <div>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Subject</th>
        <th colspan="2">Years</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>A: Historical/Social Science</td>
        <td colspan="2">2 required</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>B: English</td>
        <td colspan="2">4 required</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>C: Mathematics</td>
        <td>3 required</td>
        <td>4 recommended</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>D: Lab Science</td>
        <td>2 required</td>
        <td> 4 recommended</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>E: Language other than English</td>
        <td>2 required</td>
        <td>3 recommended</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>F: Visual and Performing Arts</td>
        <td colspan="2">1 required</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>G: College-prep Elective</td>
        <td colspan="2">1 required</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>
